{
  "stem": "14142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or-- or-- it's just when it was necessary already, then I went to-- to ask for food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I met the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, we were avoiding them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why we were in a big forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody should see us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody should hear about us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was not from our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- a boy alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were close, I mean, you know, friends, very good friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- But when the war, in '44-- when the war ended by us, actually, the Russian came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was going to come to our town to-- to meet me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was killed when the Russian were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he was going by train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a little train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how you call those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was dynamite underneath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put dynamite underneath the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it blew up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Living through the war, suffering, and when he was free-- you know, so he was killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Goleb, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yossi ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goleb. ?] And when I find out this, being in Korzec first, I didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to go away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Didn't want meet no one, anyone, anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was heartbroken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, approximately.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came back to Korzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were staying together, a few families-- families, singles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were together in one house close to the police, not far because that time, even, were people killed from the Ukraine people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were so mad because we came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we witnessed everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were living witnesses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were trying to kill us, the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So some people were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were staying in one house across the police station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
